text: Samkishya Adhikari (Nepali: समीक्षा अधिकारी, born 2005) is a female Nepalese singer. Adhikari became well-known as a singer with the release of her song "Balapan Ko Umer" in the Nepali film "Nai Nabhannu La 4." ==References== Category:Living people Category:2005 births Category:Nepalese singers
title: Samikshya Adhikari
